2011-04-03 Christian Kruse <cjk@wwwtech.de>
	* *: Completely rewrote everything ;-) Now using C++ for the
		viewers/posters and CouchDB as database interface. See
		<http://ck.kennt-wayne.de/2011/mar/classic-forum-couchdb>
		for details.

2010-07-17 Christian Kruse <cjk@wwwtech.de>
